item.title: I made this.
item.description:
I made this.

In 1996, procrastination brought me to the world wide web, one hand-coded line on HTML in emacs on a UNIX terminal login at a time. I had no idea the potent mix of a little code and a little Photoshop was going to change my life and become the start of a career of internet magic.

item.title: WTF is innovation, anyway?
item.description:
WTF is innovation, anyway?

Think about that friend who fills your social feeds with "epic" tales-their brunch outing, the art show they went to last night, the sunset they witnessed while walking the dog, and on and on. They use the term to the point of meaninglessness. When everything is epic, nothing is epic.
